OL,6,FCCTV shows the moment two customers
OL,7,Fwalk out of a restaurant without
OL,8,Fpaying after racking up a #170 bill
OL,9,Ffor a lunchtime meal.
OL,11,FThe steak and seafood restaurant near
OL,12,FPortsmouth, 'Relentless', has been
OL,13,Ftargeted dozens of times since the
OL,14,Fpandemic.
OL,16,FThe owner says the restaurant has lost
OL,17,Fnearly #10,000 to so-called 'dine and
OL,18,Fdashers', people walking out on an
OL,19,Funpaid bill.
