OL,6,FTo try and tackle the problem, it has
OL,7,Fset up a pre-payment system, but in
OL,8,Fthe recent incident, the diners paid
OL,9,Ffor their first course, then
OL,10,Feverything ordered afterwards was put
OL,11,Fon a tab.
OL,13,FScott Matthews, Owner of Relentless
OL,14,Fsaid: "They had their main courses and
OL,15,Fsaid 'oh it's lovely and we want some
OL,16,Fmore food.'
