OL,6,F"So they started to order oysters, two
OL,7,Frounds of scallops, and then another
OL,8,Flot of oysters, as well as having
OL,9,Fdouble shot spirit mixers behind the
OL,10,Fbar."
OL,12,FThe toll is not only hitting the
OL,13,Ffinances but also the staff often face
OL,14,Fabuse when trying to confront
OL,15,Fcustomers.
OL,17,F"It's disheartening for the staff
OL,18,Fbecause the staff have tried to stop
OL,19,Fthem and they would argue, saying
OL,20,F'we're not paying it', then do a
OL,21,Frunner."
